Name: Successful Logout from User Account
Precondition: The user is logged into the saucedemo Web Page
Expected Result: The user should be logged out and redirected to the login page
Test Steps:
1.Navigate to saucedemo inventory Page: 
https://www.saucedemo.com/inventory.html
2.Click on the "Logout" button on The above Left
Test Script (Step-by-Step) - Expected Re: The logout option should be visible.

Test Script (Step-by-Step) - Step: Click on the "Logout" button or link.
Test Script (Step-by-Step) - Expected Re: The user should be logged out and redirected to the login page
